{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1473/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1473.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1473/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1473/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1473/gui-resize-tool-doesnt-work-for-all-shapes"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1473/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "title": "GUI resize tool doesn't work for all shapes", "component": {"name": "gui", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/components/122878.json"}}}, "votes": 0, "watches": 2, "content": {"raw": "The [ModelManipulator](#!/osrf/gazebo/src/b20f66336eb20e92dc19b2e47c346a5f60efeea2/gazebo/gui/ModelManipulator.cc#cl-323) currently checks the visual name to determine when it can be resized, specifically looking for `unit_sphere`, `unit_cylinder`, or `unit_box`.\r\n\r\nI was recently trying to resize a box included in a world file with a different name, and I was unable to do so:\r\n~~~\r\n[Wrn] [ModelManipulator.cc:347]  Scaling is currently limited to simple shapes.\r\n~~~\r\n\r\nIs it hard to check the geometry type of a visual instead of looking at the model name?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/b20f66336eb20e92dc19b2e47c346a5f60efeea2/gazebo/gui/ModelManipulator.cc#cl-323\" rel=\"nofollow\">ModelManipulator</a> currently checks the visual name to determine when it can be resized, specifically looking for <code>unit_sphere</code>, <code>unit_cylinder</code>, or <code>unit_box</code>.</p>\n<p>I was recently trying to resize a box included in a world file with a different name, and I was unable to do so:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>[Wrn] [ModelManipulator.cc:347]  Scaling is currently limited to simple shapes.\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>Is it hard to check the geometry type of a visual instead of looking at the model name?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "state": "new", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2015-03-01T10:51:06.254201+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-06-02T23:43:37.809943+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1473}